From kevinushey at gmail.com  Wed Jun 25 21:29:22 2014
From: kevinushey at gmail.com (Kevin Ushey)
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2014 12:29:22 -0700
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] routine registration
